public enum PresenceType
extends java.lang.Enum<PresenceType>

Values for the 'type' attribute of presences, taken from RFC3921. These are only types from stanzas dealing with presence. Types used for subscriptions are enumerated in SubscriptionType even though they are both communicated via presence stanzas.

Enum Constant Summary
AVAILABLE
          Signals that an entity is online and available for communication.
PROBE
          A request for an entity's current presence.
UNAVAILABLE
          Signals that an entity is no longer available for communication.
